author: Cillian Sherlock
title: Take measures seriously, warns Irishman in China
description: An Irishman who underwent an enforced lockdown in China has said he is worried some Irish people are not taking virus prevention measures seriously.
content:
As nations around the world consider tighter restrictions on movement, an Irishman who underwent an enforced lockdown in China has said he is worried some Irish people are not taking virus prevention measures seriously.
